data.description: Well maintained home in established Harmony Hills. Great central location. No carpet! Laminate, Linoleum and Ceramic tiled floors. Well done converted garage with crown molding makes great family room. Large covered 13 x 12 ceramic tiled patio overlooks shady back yard with mature pecan trees. Gazebo & Storage shed. CF light cover in bfast, window scarves/treatments in LR, Den & back bedroom do not convey.Brokered And Advertised By: Elaine Ludwig Real Estate CompListing Agent: Carla Haley
